            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;     欧洲股市早段下跌。英国富时100指数报9,674.50点，跌17.08点(0.18%)；德国DAX指数报23,723.05点，跌3.17点(0.01%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,085.94点，跌10.49点(0.13%)。 <br/>(WL)</span>\n</div>",
